                                ]

                                tokenizer = "split_on_colon_tokenizer"
                            }
                            standard_case_sensitive           = {
                                filter    = []
                                tokenizer = "standard"
                                type      = "custom"
                            }

                            colon_to_hyphen_filter = {
                                mappings = [
                                    ": => -",
                                ]
                                type     = "mapping"
                            }
                            hyphen_to_colon_filter = {
                                mappings = [
                                    "- => :",
                                ]
                                type     = "mapping"
                            }
                        }
                        filter      = {
                            autocomplete-filter = {
                                max_gram = "20"
                                min_gram = "2"
                                type     = "edge_ngram"
                            }
                            truncate_20         = {
                                length = "20"
                                type   = "truncate"
                            }
                        }
                        normalizer  = {
                            legacy_short_key_normalizer = {
                                char_filter = [
                                    "colon_to_hyphen_filter",
                                ]
                                type        = "custom"
                            }
                            lowercase_norm              = {
                                char_filter = []
                                filter      = [
                                    "lowercase",
                                ]
                                type        = "custom"
                            }
                            short_key_normalizer        = {
                                char_filter = [
                                    "hyphen_to_colon_filter",
                                ]
                                type        = "custom"
                            }
                        }
                        tokenizer   = {
                            autocomplete-tokenizer             = {
                                tokenize_on_chars = [
                                    "whitespace",
                                    "-",
                                    "_",
                                ]
                                type              = "char_group"
                            }
                            participant_phone_number_tokenizer = {
                                max_gram = "20"
                                min_gram = "6"
                                type     = "edge_ngram"
                            }
                            split_on_colon_tokenizer           = {
                                group   = "1"
                                pattern = "([a-zA-Z]+):.*"
                                type    = "pattern"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    lifecycle          = {
                        name = "v4-lifecycle"
                    }
                    mapping            = {
                        nested_objects = {
                            limit = "50000"
                        }
                    }
                    number_of_replicas = "1"
                    number_of_shards   = "6"
                    refresh_interval   = "30s"
                    routing            = {
                        allocation = {
                            include = {
                                _tier_preference = "data_content,data_hot"
                            }
                        }
                    }
                    search             = {
                        slowlog = {
                            level     = "info"
                            threshold = {
                                fetch = {
                                    info = "200ms"
                                    warn = "1s"
                                }
                                query = {
                                    info = "2s"
                                    warn = "5s"
                                }
                            }
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    )
    id   = "dialpad-v4"
    name = "dialpad-v4"

    dataset_id               = "data_science"
    deletion_protection      = true
    description              = "Aggregate of all behavior results for models. This view should be queried instead of any versioned behaviors_vX tables."

    id                       = "voiceai-staging:data_science.behaviors"

        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "datascience"

        "table"     = "behaviors"

    max_staleness            = null
    num_bytes                = 0
    num_long_term_bytes      = 0

    require_partition_filter = false
    resource_tags            = {}
    schema                   = jsonencode(
        [
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "call_id"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "call_leg_id"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "call_side"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "created_at"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },

                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "org"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "STRING"

                type = "STRING"
            },

                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "runner_version"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "behavior_type"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "behavior_end"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "behavior_value"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "processed_at"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "model_mode"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "company"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "emitted"
                type = "BOOLEAN"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "PARTITIONTIME"
                type = "TIMESTAMP"
            },
        ]
    )
    self_link                = "https://bigquery.googleapis.com/bigquery/v2/projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/data_science/tables/behaviors"
    table_id                 = "behaviors"
    terraform_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "datascience"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "behaviors"
        "team"      = "ai_nlp"
    }
    type                     = "VIEW"

    view {
        query          = <<-EOT
            # N.B. we need to list all fields rather than `select *` to support removing
            # columns between versions.
            #
            # As the column names will be generated from the first use of each column, be
            # sure the earliest chunk of this view query either is the table with the
            # superset of all columns or has made use of `AS` statements to give the
            # correct names.
            
            SELECT
              call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              org,
              source,
              model_name,
              model_package,
              model_version,
              runner_version,
              behavior_type,
              behavior_end,
              behavior_value,
              processed_at,
              "" AS model_mode,  -- deprecated in v4
              company,
              emitted,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v4`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v3`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- company -- v3 last field
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v2`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- model_mode -- v2 last field
              NULL, -- company -- v3 last field
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v1`
        EOT
        use_legacy_sql = false
    }
}

                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "voiceai_id"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "kind"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "channel"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "read_codec"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "read_channels"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "read_sample_rate"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "PARTITIONTIME"
                type = "TIMESTAMP"
            },
        ]
    )
    self_link                = "https://bigquery.googleapis.com/bigquery/v2/projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/data_science/tables/calldata"
    table_id                 = "calldata"
    terraform_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "datascience"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "calldata"
        "team"      = "ai_ds"
    }
    type                     = "VIEW"

    view {
        query          = <<-EOT
            # N.B. we need to list all fields rather than `select *` to support removing
            # columns between versions.
            #
            # As the column names will be generated from the first use of each column, be
            # sure the earliest chunk of this view query either is the table with the
            # superset of all columns or has made use of `AS` statements to give the
            # correct names.
            
            SELECT
              *,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.calldata_v3`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              -- v3
              NULL, -- read_codec
              NULL, -- read_channels
              NULL, -- read_sample_rate
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.calldata_v2`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              -- v2
              "call" AS kind,
              "mod_voiceai" AS channel,
              -- v3
              NULL, -- read_codec
              NULL, -- read_channels
              NULL, -- read_sample_rate
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.calldata_v1`
        EOT
        use_legacy_sql = false
    }
}

# module.gcp.google_bigquery_table.gcs_current_bucket_costs:
resource "google_bigquery_table" "gcs_current_bucket_costs" {
    creation_time            = 1717167871332
    dataset_id               = "billing"
    deletion_protection      = false
    description              = "Summary view for gcs_* raw data"
    effective_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "billing"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "gcs-current-bucket-costs"
        "team"      = "ai_eng"
    }
    etag                     = "IklqAZQtAyY84vPW2FFomQ=="
    expiration_time          = 0
    friendly_name            = null
    id                       = "projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/billing/tables/gcs_current_bucket_costs"
    labels                   = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "billing"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "gcs-current-bucket-costs"
        "team"      = "ai_eng"
    }
    last_modified_time       = 1725460153145
    location                 = "US"
    max_staleness            = null
    num_bytes                = 0
    num_long_term_bytes      = 0
    num_rows                 = 0
    project                  = "voiceai-staging"
    require_partition_filter = false
    resource_tags            = {}
    schema                   = jsonencode(
        [
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "bucket_name"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "size_GB"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "object_count"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "avg_obj_per_GB"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_class_a_price"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_class_b_price"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_retrieval_fee"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "class_a_count"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "class_b_count"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "replication_price"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_obj_replications"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_location"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_SC"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_cost_at_rest"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_operations_costs"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_replication_costs"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "current_total_costs"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
        ]
    )
    self_link                = "https://bigquery.googleapis.com/bigquery/v2/projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/billing/tables/gcs_current_bucket_costs"
    table_id                 = "gcs_current_bucket_costs"
    terraform_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "billing"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "gcs-current-bucket-costs"
        "team"      = "ai_eng"
    }
    type                     = "VIEW"

    view {
        query          = <<-EOT
            SELECT
                *,
                current_cost_at_rest + current_operations_costs + current_replication_costs AS current_total_costs
            FROM (
                SELECT
                    B.bucket_name,
                    B.size_GB,
                    B.object_count,
                    B.avg_obj_per_GB,
                    BC.price_class_a AS current_class_a_price,
                    BC.price_class_b AS current_class_b_price,
                    BC.retrieval_fee AS current_retrieval_fee,
                    OP.class_a_count,
                    OP.class_b_count,
                    R.replication_price,
                    R.obj_replications_30d AS current_obj_replications,
                    BC.location AS current_location,
                    BC.storage_class AS current_SC,
                    (BC.price_at_rest * B.size_GB) AS current_cost_at_rest,
                    (OP.class_a_count / 1000 * BC.price_class_a + OP.class_b_count / 1000 * BC.price_class_b) AS current_operations_costs,
                    IFNULL(R.obj_replications_30d / B.avg_obj_per_GB * R.replication_price, 0) AS current_replication_costs
                FROM `voiceai-staging.billing.gcs_buckets` AS B
                INNER JOIN `voiceai-staging.billing.gcs_bucket_config` AS BC
                ON B.config_id = BC.config_id
                INNER JOIN `voiceai-staging.billing.gcs_operations` AS OP
                ON B.bucket_name = OP.bucket_name
                LEFT JOIN `voiceai-staging.billing.gcs_replications` AS R
                ON B.bucket_name = R.bucket_name
            )
        EOT
        use_legacy_sql = false
    }
}

        [
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "STRING"

                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "call_leg_id"
                type = "STRING"

                type = "STRING"

                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "INTEGER"

                mode = "NULLABLE"

                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "source"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "model_name"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "model_package"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "model_version"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "runner_version"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "event_type"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "event_start"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "event_end"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "event_probability"
                type = "FLOAT"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "event_extra"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "processed_at"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "model_mode"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "company"
                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "emitted"
                type = "BOOLEAN"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "PARTITIONTIME"
                type = "TIMESTAMP"
            },
        ]
    )
    self_link                = "https://bigquery.googleapis.com/bigquery/v2/projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/data_science/tables/model_events"
    table_id                 = "model_events"
    terraform_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "datascience"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "model-events"
        "team"      = "ai_nlp"
    }
    type                     = "VIEW"

    view {
        query          = <<-EOT
            # N.B. we need to list all fields rather than `select *` to support removing
            # columns between versions.
            #
            # As the column names will be generated from the first use of each column, be
            # sure the earliest chunk of this view query either is the table with the
            # superset of all columns or has made use of `AS` statements to give the
            # correct names.
            SELECT
              metadata.call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              org,
              metadata.source,
              model_name,
              model_package,
              model_version,
              runner_version,
              event_type,
              event_start,
              event_end,
              event_probability,
              pii.event_extra,
              processed_at,
              "" AS model_mode,  -- deprecated in v4
              company,
              emitted,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM metadata._PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v5` AS metadata
            LEFT JOIN `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_pii_v1` AS pii
            USING (event_id)
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              org,
              source,
              model_name,
              model_package,
              model_version,
              runner_version,
              event_type,
              event_start,
              event_end,
              event_probability,
              event_extra,
              processed_at,
              "" AS model_mode,  -- deprecated in v4
              company,
              emitted,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v4`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v3`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- company -- v3 last field
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v2`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              *,
              NULL, -- model_mode -- v2 last field
              NULL, -- company -- v3 last field
              NULL, -- emitted -- v4 last field
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v1`
        EOT
        use_legacy_sql = false
    }
}

            },

                type = "STRING"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "read_channels"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "read_sample_rate"
                type = "INTEGER"
            },
            {
                mode = "NULLABLE"
                name = "PARTITIONTIME"
                type = "TIMESTAMP"
            },
        ]
    )
    self_link                = "https://bigquery.googleapis.com/bigquery/v2/projects/voiceai-staging/datasets/data_science/tables/tastes"
    table_id                 = "tastes"
    terraform_labels         = {
        "component" = "ai"
        "dataset"   = "datascience"
        "feature"   = "internal"
        "table"     = "tastes"
        "team"      = "ai_ds"
    }
    type                     = "VIEW"

    view {
        query          = <<-EOT
            # N.B. we need to list all fields rather than `select *` to support removing
            # columns between versions.
            #
            # As the column names will be generated from the first use of each column, be
            # sure the earliest chunk of this view query either is the table with the
            # superset of all columns or has made use of `AS` statements to give the
            # correct names.
            
            SELECT
              -- metadata v1
              metadata.call_id,
              metadata.call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              `group` as `group`,
              org,
              metadata.source,
              user,
              audio_wav_directory IS NOT NULL AS has_audio,
              asr_model_name,
              asr_model_version,
              formatter_model_version,
              punctuator_model_version,
              -- pii V1
              pii.raw,
              pii.final,
              -- metadata v2
              direction,
              orientation,
              contact,
              locale,
              organizer_user,
              organizer_office,
              organizer_company,
              participant_user,
              participant_office,
              participant_company,
              -- metadata v3
              duration,
              tastes_json_url,
              "" AS transcripts_ctm_url,
              "" AS audio_wav_url,
              -- metadata v4
              country,
              device,
              license,
              -- metadata v5
              company,
              -- metadata v6
              ended_at,
              audio_wav_directory,
              sip_call_id,
              decoder_ip,
              client_ip,
              interrupted,
              -- metadata v7
              kind,
              channel,
              -- metadata v8
              audio_transmission_format,
              IF(
                audio_wav_directory IS NOT NULL,
                SAFE_CAST(
                  regexp_extract(audio_transmission_format, '\\d+') AS INT64
                ),
                NULL
              ) AS audio_samplerate,
              read_codec,
              read_channels,
              read_sample_rate,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM metadata._PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_v9` AS metadata
            LEFT JOIN `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_pii_v1` AS pii
            USING (call_id, call_leg_id, source)
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              -- v1
              call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              `group` as `group`,
              org,
              source,
              user,
              audio_wav_directory IS NOT NULL AS has_audio,
              asr_model_name,
              asr_model_version,
              formatter_model_version,
              punctuator_model_version,
              raw,
              final,
              -- v2
              direction,
              orientation,
              contact,
              locale,
              organizer_user,
              organizer_office,
              organizer_company,
              participant_user,
              participant_office,
              participant_company,
              -- v3
              duration,
              tastes_json_url,
              "" AS transcripts_ctm_url,
              "" AS audio_wav_url,
              -- v4
              country,
              device,
              license,
              -- v5
              company,
              -- v6
              ended_at,
              audio_wav_directory,
              sip_call_id,
              decoder_ip,
              client_ip,
              interrupted,
              -- v7
              kind,
              channel,
              -- v8
              audio_transmission_format,
              IF(
                audio_wav_directory IS NOT NULL,
                SAFE_CAST(
                  regexp_extract(audio_transmission_format, '\\d+') AS INT64
                ),
                NULL
              ) AS audio_samplerate,
              read_codec,
              read_channels,
              read_sample_rate,
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_v8`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              -- v1
              call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              `group` as `group`,
              org,
              source,
              user,
              audio_wav_directory IS NOT NULL AS has_audio,
              asr_model_name,
              asr_model_version,
              formatter_model_version,
              punctuator_model_version,
              raw,
              final,
              -- v2
              direction,
              orientation,
              contact,
              locale,
              organizer_user,
              organizer_office,
              organizer_company,
              participant_user,
              participant_office,
              participant_company,
              -- v3
              duration,
              tastes_json_url,
              "" AS transcripts_ctm_url,
              "" AS audio_wav_url,
              -- v4
              country,
              device,
              license,
              -- v5
              company,
              -- v6
              ended_at,
              audio_wav_directory,
              sip_call_id,
              decoder_ip,
              client_ip,
              interrupted,
              -- v7
              kind,
              channel,
              -- v8
              "PCMU/8000" AS audio_transmission_format,
              8000 AS audio_samplerate,
              NULL, -- read_codec
              NULL, -- read_channels
              NULL, -- read_sample_rate
              TIMESTAMP(EXTRACT(DATE FROM _PARTITIONTIME)) AS PARTITIONTIME
            FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_v7`
            
            UNION ALL
            
            SELECT
              -- v1
              call_id,
              call_leg_id,
              call_side,
              created_at,
              `group` as `group`,

# module.gcp.module.realtime.module.gke-realtime-us-central1.data.google_project.project:

    folder_id        = "363350336823"

                  - value: pre-release

                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1

                name: vertex-summarization
                selector: kind=nlp,variant=vertex-summarization
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 20
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                downscaleRamp: 0.2
                maximum: 175
                minimum: 1
            ---
            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: nlp
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: 0e01e7e6ba
                variant: vertex-summarization-actionitem
              name: nlp-vertex-summarization-actionitem
            spec:
              deployment:
                label: realtime-runner
                name: vertex-summarization-actionitem
                selector: kind=nlp,variant=vertex-summarization-actionitem
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 20
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                downscaleRamp: 0.2
                maximum: 175
                minimum: 1
            ---
            apiVersion: v1

            metadata:

        EOT
        "realtime-registration.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'
                perInstance: 20
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                appname: SET_BY_VARIANTS_TOOLING
                kind: ctm
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: "5552152162"
                variant: ctm
              name: ctm-ctm
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: ctm
                selector: kind=ctm,variant=ctm
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release

              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1

        "realtime-egress-variants.yaml"     = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: autoscaler.talkiq.com/v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: egress
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: 8d2750fe14
                variant: egress
              name: egress-egress
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: egress
                selector: kind=egress,variant=egress
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1
        EOT

        "realtime-healthcheck.yaml"         = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: healthcheck
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=healthcheck
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                selector: "default:kind=decoder"
                perInstance: 125
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

                upscaleLimit: 50

        "realtime-registration.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'
                perInstance: 20
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

        "BUCKET_TASTES"                     = "voiceai-staging-tastes-v4"

        "PUBSUB_REDIS_HOST"                 = "redis.realtime.talkiq.com"
        "PUBSUB_REDIS_PORT"                 = "6379"
    }

    binary_data = {}
    data        = {
        "realtime-ctm-variants.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                appname: SET_BY_VARIANTS_TOOLING
                kind: ctm
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: "5552152162"
                variant: ctm
              name: ctm-ctm
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: ctm
                selector: kind=ctm,variant=ctm
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1

                  groups:

                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50

                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1

            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: nlp
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: 0e01e7e6ba
                variant: voicemail-regex
              name: nlp-voicemail-regex
            spec:
              deployment:
                label: realtime-runner
                name: voicemail-regex
                selector: kind=nlp,variant=voicemail-regex
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 68
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                downscaleRamp: 0.2
                maximum: 51.470588235294116
                minimum: 1
        EOT
        "realtime-registration.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'
                perInstance: 20
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

        resource_version = "14436"
        uid              = "17ff8739-2a42-4479-97bd-2f3ad2185ece"
    }
}

# module.gcp.module.realtime.module.k8s-realtime-us-west1.kubernetes_config_map.autoscaler_configd:
resource "kubernetes_config_map" "autoscaler_configd" {
    binary_data = {}
    data        = {
        "realtime-ctm-variants.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                appname: SET_BY_VARIANTS_TOOLING
                kind: ctm
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: "5552152162"
                variant: ctm
              name: ctm-ctm
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: ctm
                selector: kind=ctm,variant=ctm
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1
        EOT

        "realtime-egress-variants.yaml"     = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: autoscaler.talkiq.com/v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: egress
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: 8d2750fe14
                variant: egress
              name: egress-egress
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: egress
                selector: kind=egress,variant=egress
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1
        EOT

                - 30     3-17   1-5  1.5
                - 31     3-17   1-5  1.4
                - 32     3-17   1-5  1.3
                - 33     3-17   1-5  1.2
                - 34     3-17   1-5  1.1
                timezone: "-08:00"
        EOT
        "realtime-healthcheck.yaml"         = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: healthcheck
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=healthcheck
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                selector: "default:kind=decoder"
                perInstance: 125
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT
        "realtime-informer.yaml"            = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: informer
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=informer
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:informer:8080'
                perInstance: 40
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

        "realtime-registration.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'
                perInstance: 20
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

resource "kubernetes_config_map" "autoscaler_configd" {
    binary_data = {}
    data        = {
        "realtime-ctm-variants.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                appname: SET_BY_VARIANTS_TOOLING
                kind: ctm
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: "5552152162"
                variant: ctm
              name: ctm-ctm
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: ctm
                selector: kind=ctm,variant=ctm
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1
        EOT
        "realtime-decoder-variants.yaml"    = <<-EOT

                  groups:

                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:

                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1

        "realtime-registration.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'

                upscaleLimit: 50

        "realtime-ctm-variants.yaml"        = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                appname: SET_BY_VARIANTS_TOOLING
                kind: ctm
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: "5552152162"
                variant: ctm
              name: ctm-ctm
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: ctm
                selector: kind=ctm,variant=ctm
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1

            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: decoder
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: ffbd6f192a
                variant: nemo-es-es
              name: decoder-nemo-es-es
            spec:
              deployment:
                label: decoder
                name: decoder-nemo-es-es
                selector: kind=decoder,variant=nemo-es-es
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release

                type: gke-multi
              interval: 10
              metric:
                backlog: 1

        "realtime-egress-variants.yaml"     = <<-EOT
            apiVersion: autoscaler.talkiq.com/v1
            kind: Autoscaler
            metadata:
              annotations:
                kind: egress
                project: voiceai-staging
                tag: 8d2750fe14
                variant: egress
              name: egress-egress
            spec:
              deployment:
                name: egress
                selector: kind=egress,variant=egress
                split:
                  groups:
                  - default: true
                    value: release
                  label: stage
                type: gke-multi
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                perInstance: 400
                selector: default:kind=decoder
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 5
                minimum: 1
        EOT

        "realtime-healthcheck.yaml"         = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: healthcheck
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=healthcheck
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gke.replicas_multi_sum
                selector: "default:kind=decoder"
                perInstance: 125
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT
        "realtime-informer.yaml"            = <<-EOT
            - deployment:
                name: informer
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=informer
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:informer:8080'
                perInstance: 40
                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

            - deployment:
                name: registration
                type: gke-multi
                selector: kind=registration
                split:
                  label: stage
                  groups:
                  - value: release
                    default: true
                  - value: canary
                    proportion: 0.1
                  - value: pre-release
                    proportion: 0.50
              metric:
                namespace: gcp.mci_per_backend_request_count
                selector: 'default:realtime-registration-multicluster-service:8080'

                style: tasks
              scaleConfig:
                maximum: 20
                minimum: 1
                downscaleDelay: 3
                downscaleRamp: 0.25
                downscaleLimit: 25
                upscaleLimit: 50
        EOT

# module.gcp.module.retention.google_bigquery_data_transfer_config.query_config["behaviors_v1"]:
resource "google_bigquery_data_transfer_config" "query_config" {
    data_refresh_window_days  = 0
    data_source_id            = "scheduled_query"
    destination_dataset_id    = null
    disabled                  = false
    display_name              = "bq_retention_behaviors_v1"
    id                        = "projects/397406432431/locations/us/transferConfigs/61b65da9-0000-280c-8329-582429a78ab8"
    location                  = "US"
    name                      = "projects/397406432431/locations/us/transferConfigs/61b65da9-0000-280c-8329-582429a78ab8"
    notification_pubsub_topic = null
    params                    = {
        "query" = <<-EOT
            BEGIN
                DECLARE fulfillment_name STRING;
            
                SET fulfillment_name = "bq_behaviors_v1";
            
                # PREPARE A LIST OF ALL TIME TO BE DELETED RECORDS
                CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE delete_list(
                    pt TIMESTAMP,
                    call_id STRING,
                    source STRING
                ) AS (
                    SELECT target._PARTITIONTIME as pt,
                           target.call_id,
                           target.source
                    FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v1` AS target
                    JOIN `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_requests` AS requests
                    USING (source, call_id)
                    WHERE target._PARTITIONTIME <= TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), DAY)
                );
            
                # DELETE
                DELETE
                FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.behaviors_v1` AS target
                WHERE EXISTS(
                        SELECT * FROM delete_list AS requests
                        WHERE target.call_id = requests.call_id
                        AND target.source = requests.source
                ) AND target._PARTITIONTIME IN (
                    SELECT pt FROM delete_list
                );
            
                # WRITE DOWN EVERYTHING THAT HAS BEEN DELETED
                INSERT `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_fulfillments_v1` (call_id, source, created_at, resource_name)
                SELECT call_id,
                       source,
                       UNIX_MILLIS(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()),
                       fulfillment_name
                FROM delete_list;
            END
        EOT
    }
    project                   = "voiceai-staging"
    schedule                  = "every day 07:00"
    service_account_name      = "app-bigquery@voiceai-staging.iam.gserviceaccount.com"
}

    display_name              = "bq_retention_model_events_v2"

                    SELECT target._PARTITIONTIME as pt,
                           target.call_id,

                );

                INSERT `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_fulfillments_v1` (call_id, source, created_at, resource_name)
                SELECT call_id,
                       source,
                       UNIX_MILLIS(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()),
                       fulfillment_name
                FROM delete_list;
            END
        EOT
    }
    project                   = "voiceai-staging"
    schedule                  = "every day 07:00"
    service_account_name      = "app-bigquery@voiceai-staging.iam.gserviceaccount.com"

# module.gcp.module.retention.google_bigquery_data_transfer_config.query_config["model_events_v3"]:
resource "google_bigquery_data_transfer_config" "query_config" {
    data_refresh_window_days  = 0
    data_source_id            = "scheduled_query"
    destination_dataset_id    = null
    disabled                  = false
    display_name              = "bq_retention_model_events_v3"
    id                        = "projects/397406432431/locations/us/transferConfigs/679a91dd-0000-2482-9b4b-c82add7a23f8"
    location                  = "US"
    name                      = "projects/397406432431/locations/us/transferConfigs/679a91dd-0000-2482-9b4b-c82add7a23f8"
    notification_pubsub_topic = null
    params                    = {
        "query" = <<-EOT
            BEGIN
                DECLARE fulfillment_name STRING;
            
                SET fulfillment_name = "bq_model_events_v3";
            
                # PREPARE A LIST OF ALL TIME TO BE DELETED RECORDS
                CREATE TEMPORARY TABLE delete_list(
                    pt TIMESTAMP,
                    call_id STRING,
                    source STRING
                ) AS (
                    SELECT target._PARTITIONTIME as pt,
                           target.call_id,
                           target.source
                    FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v3` AS target
                    JOIN `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_requests` AS requests
                    USING (source, call_id)
                    WHERE target._PARTITIONTIME <= TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), DAY)
                );
            
                # DELETE
                DELETE
                FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.model_events_v3` AS target
                WHERE EXISTS(
                        SELECT * FROM delete_list AS requests
                        WHERE target.call_id = requests.call_id
                        AND target.source = requests.source
                ) AND target._PARTITIONTIME IN (
                    SELECT pt FROM delete_list
                );
            
                # WRITE DOWN EVERYTHING THAT HAS BEEN DELETED
                INSERT `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_fulfillments_v1` (call_id, source, created_at, resource_name)
                SELECT call_id,
                       source,

                    call_id STRING,
                    source STRING
                ) AS (
                    SELECT target._PARTITIONTIME as pt,
                           target.call_id,
                           target.source
                    FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_v8` AS target
                    JOIN `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_requests` AS requests
                    USING (source, call_id)
                    WHERE target._PARTITIONTIME <= TIMESTAMP_TRUNC(TIMESTAMP_SUB(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(), INTERVAL 1 DAY), DAY)
                );
            
                # DELETE
                DELETE
                FROM `voiceai-staging.data_science.tastes_v8` AS target
                WHERE EXISTS(
                        SELECT * FROM delete_list AS requests
                        WHERE target.call_id = requests.call_id
                        AND target.source = requests.source
                ) AND target._PARTITIONTIME IN (
                    SELECT pt FROM delete_list
                );
            
                # WRITE DOWN EVERYTHING THAT HAS BEEN DELETED
                INSERT `voiceai-staging.data_science.retention_fulfillments_v1` (call_id, source, created_at, resource_name)
                SELECT call_id,
                       source,
                       UNIX_MILLIS(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP()),
                       fulfillment_name
                FROM delete_list;
            END
        EOT
    }
    project                   = "voiceai-staging"
    schedule                  = "every day 07:00"
    service_account_name      = "app-bigquery@voiceai-staging.iam.gserviceaccount.com"
}

    effective_labels             = {
